name: Town Jjhief
content: Oh, You are…!

name: Town Jjhief
content: ……Squeak.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Wait. I can't believe…

name: Town Jjhief
content: The town is in chaos these days... I need to be sure you're the heir to 'that family'.

name: Town Jjhief
content: The Exam monster is very scary. It may have sent a subordinate.

name: Town Jjhief
content: ……Squeak.

name: Town Jjhief
content: You have to answer some of my questions. It is a test.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Then… just simple questions.

name: Town Jjhief
content: If the town becomes peaceful, where do you want to go for your summer vacation?

name: Town Jjhief
content: What season do you like? Except summer.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Squeak, Squeak… I'm getting to know… Then, what is your favorite fruit?

name: Town Jjhief
content: In our town's field, what catches your eyes?

name: Town Jjhief
content: ……Squeak.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Oh, You are…!

name: Town Jjhief
content: <color=#a9ad35>The heir to the Doe Habeoreoseu family!</color>

name: Town Jjhief
content: <color=#479dda>The heir to the Pebeureo family!</color>

name: Town Jjhief
content: <color=#bf4240>The heir to the Gopaebureoseu family!</color>

name: Town Jjhief
content: Okay. I believe you.

name: Town Jjhief
content: But I can't designate you as Mathranger right now.

name: Town Jjhief
content: As you know, our town is in danger because the Exam monster was unsealed.

name: Town Jjhief
content: At first, it aimed for school. But now, it aims for the town center too.

name: Town Jjhief
content: Mathranger is, squeak, an important role to succeed wise men who have sealed the Exam monster in the past.

name: Town Jjhief
content: I can't designate it to anyone!!!!!

name: Town Jjhief
content: …So, I will test your qualification for the Mathranger.

name: Town Jjhief
content: You must be honest with your own ability. Squeak!
